---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Legal Disclaimer — Nick Battaglia"
  description="Disclaimer for Argus and nickvbattaglia.com: AI outputs are not legal advice."
>

  <section class="container pt-20 pb-16 max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-light text-text mb-8">Legal Disclaimer</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-text-dim leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-text">Not legal advice.</strong> Argus and all content on
        nickvbattaglia.com are provided for informational and demonstration purposes only.
        Nothing on this site or produced by the Argus tool constitutes legal advice,
        creates an attorney-client relationship, or should be relied upon as a substitute
        for consultation with a licensed attorney.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-text">AI-generated outputs.</strong> Argus uses large language
        models to generate, revise, and analyze contract language. AI-generated outputs may
        be inaccurate, incomplete, or inappropriate for your specific circumstances. All
        AI-generated content should be reviewed by a qualified legal professional before
        use in any transaction or legal matter.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-text">Privilege and confidentiality.</strong> Do not enter
        privileged communications, confidential client information, or personally identifiable
        information into Argus or any other consumer AI tool. Courts have held that
        disclosure of attorney communications to third-party AI services may constitute
        waiver of attorney-client privilege and work-product protection. Argus's PII
        firewall and anonymizer reduce but do not eliminate this risk.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-text">Inadvertent waiver risk.</strong> The attorney-client
        privilege protects confidential communications between attorneys and clients made
        for the purpose of obtaining legal advice. Sharing such communications with
        third-party services — including AI tools — may constitute a waiver of that
        privilege, rendering the communications discoverable in litigation or regulatory
        proceedings. Work-product doctrine protections may similarly be eroded by
        disclosure to non-agents.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-text">No warranty.</strong> Argus is provided "as is"
        without warranty of any kind, express or implied. Use is at your own risk.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-text">Governing law.</strong> This disclaimer is governed by
        the laws of the State of Indiana without regard to conflict-of-law principles.
      </p>

      <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-8">Last updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
